fc1 = Linear(4, 2)()
fc2 = Linear(4, 2)()
cadd = CAddTable()([fc1, fc2])
preprocessor = Model([fc1, fc2], [cadd])
relu = ReLU()()
fc3 = Linear(2, 1)(relu)
trainable = Model([relu], [fc3])
model = Model(preprocessor, trainable)
model.forward([np.array([0.1, 0.2, -0.3, -0.4]), np.array([0.5, 0.4, -0.2, 
    -0.1])])
model.backward([np.array([0.1, 0.2, -0.3, -0.4]), np.array([0.5, 0.4, -0.2,
    -0.1])], np.array([1.0]))
